---
title: Cherry & Balsamic-Glazed Lamb with Roast Potatoes & Radish Salad
description: Oh, happy days! With a heavenly combination of golden roasted potatoes paired with a crisp radish salad and a tangy-sweet cherry
and balsamic glaze drizzled over the lamb rump, this is a modern and delicious union that will be lovingly devoured by all.

 *This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
